OL,3,CThe wildfire the size of 210 football
OL,4,Cpitches that is burning at 600 degrees
OL,6,FA wildfire in at Clydach Dingle, near
OL,7,FBrynmawr, has spread across an area of
OL,8,F150 hectares, the equivalent of 210
OL,9,Ffootball pitches, and has reached the
OL,10,Fvicinity of an underground gas pipe.
OL,12,FThe fire, which has been ongoing for
OL,13,Ffour weeks, has been described by
OL,14,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Services
OL,15,Fas a "complex incident" with crews
OL,16,Fusing specialist equipment to contain
OL,17,Fthe spread.
