OL,6,FIn a statement, the service has
OL,7,Fconfirmed there is no immediate risk
OL,8,Fto life or property, but advise
OL,9,Fresidents living nearby to keep their
OL,10,Fdoors and windows closed when smoke is
OL,11,Fpresent.
OL,13,FThe cause of the fire is still under
OL,14,Finvestigation.
