OL,6,FMatt Jones, Head of Operations for
OL,7,FSWFR, said: "The fire is a very
OL,8,Fcomplex deep-seated incidence, which
OL,9,Fhas been challenging for our teams to
OL,10,Faddress, as a result we are using a
OL,11,Fmultitude of techniques to address the
OL,12,Fissue.
OL,14,F"We are working in close partnership
OL,15,Fwith Gwent Police, the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment, the local authorities and
OL,17,FNatural Resources Wales to implement a
OL,18,Fmulti-agency strategy."
