OL,6,FHe also said that due to the nature of
OL,7,Fthe fire, typical methods such as
OL,8,Fusing a helicopter to dump water over
OL,9,Fthe fire would not work.
OL,11,FNational Gas has reassured nearby
OL,12,Fresidents that the risk to the gas
OL,13,Fpipeline near the fire is currently
OL,14,Flow.
