OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Our teams have been working closely
OL,8,Fwith local emergency services, local
OL,9,Fgas distribution networks and all
OL,10,Fother partners to assess any potential
OL,11,Fimpacts to the supply of gas or any
OL,12,Fhealth and safety risks.
OL,14,FOur initial assessment since being
OL,15,Fmade aware is that the risk of any
OL,16,Fdisruption to the supply of gas or any
OL,17,Fassociated health and safety risks is
OL,18,Fvery low."
